<h2>ABOUT</h2>
<h3>Location</h3>
<p>Greenwood/Greenbriar is a residential area located in the Northwestern region of Calgary. At the south, it is bound by the Trans-Canada Highway and at the north, the Bow River. At the west, it&rsquo;s bound by Stoney Trial and in the east, the Bowness community. The neighborhood is currently represented by the Ward 1 Councilor at the Calgary City Council.</p>
<h3>Demographics</h3>
<p>The 2012 Greenwood/Greenbriar demographics indicate the town&rsquo;s population to be 946 settled within 501 homes. The population density is calculated to be 790/kilometer square. The overall land area is measured to be 1.2 kilometer square.</p>
</div>
